Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 10:45:22 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 28/73] Serve PDF chrome resources
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The viewer knocked on chrome’s old door,
We gave just resources, nothing more.
Now APIs grumble next in line.
